{"tid":1656662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[置頂] 我哋應該同班台灣狗割蓆！勿被帶風向！","createTime":"2019-10-15T16:58:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T17:32:55.000Z","uid":73381,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"043e88fc79fe339e06d9cfabaab62d49c057aa94","tid":1656662,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:58:28.000Z","msg":"EU同美國都唔支持加泰獨立 我哋香港自己都未搞掂,搞乜撚嘢加泰呀 好撚得閒？<br />\n到時美帝同EU反面就仆街啦<br />\n對加泰立場只需冷處理<br />\n<br />\n同樣 美國唔支持台灣獨立<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">美國政府採取「一個中國政策」（One-China Policy）作為外交政策。<br />\n對於台灣，則依據台灣關係法及六項保證為方針，則<span style=\"color: red;\">不承認台灣是獨立國家</span>，但承諾對台灣提供軍售。</span><br />\n<br />\n照你哋咁講 我哋係唔係應該同台灣割埋蓆？一陣話我哋撐台獨影響法案通過就唔好啦"},{"pid":"48d635da22c11a04bfe89967b21061569515af1b","tid":1656662,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:58:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/afoWPNY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FafoWPNY.jpg&h=041452ea&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"90e9986470a121a0e5ed6d574b54593c4020743c","tid":1656662,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:59:09.000Z","msg":"【簡易文宣】本土國際戰線&mdash;Facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656652\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656652</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b0bf6df8f3eaf98e7d83fddfbb7ba845f046c36f","tid":1656662,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:00:33.000Z","msg":"支持同加泰割蓆嘅入黎講兩句？"},{"pid":"b8adf130dd6fec0159d9ff8585bb91f619189111","tid":1656662,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:02:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca250a7743972bcfeb4e00bb32a68f30dd4d4a92","tid":1656662,"uid":81698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:03:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/c